Nanomaterials-based Flexible Wireless System to Monitor and Record Biosignals from Human Motions
# MXene Biosignal Monitor

## Overview

This project simulates a biosignal monitoring system using MXene sensors. It includes dummy data and basic signal processing.

## Features

- Flask web interface
- Dummy sensor data simulation
- Simple signal filtering

## Setup

1. Clone the repository.
2. Navigate to the project directory.
3. Install dependencies:

   bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
